<plot>Hosted by President and Mrs. Reagan, this concert in the PBS series "In Performance at the White House" featured performances by five great ladies of the theater. It included a tribute to Mary Martin's 50th anniversary in show business. Haerd here are "My Heart Belongs to Daddy", "And I Am Telling You", "Don't Cry for Me, Argentina", and "Memory" and other selections.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?262004</url></doc>
